---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import HeroBanner from '../components/HeroBanner.vue';
import PageSection from '../components/PageSection.vue';
---

<Layout title="Sh!t" description="A simple Astro site example">
	<HeroBanner
		data-section-color="#d3a6fe"
	>
		<h1 slot="heading">
			One time I said the word
			<span class="highlight">Sh!t</span>
			during an interviewðŸ™€.
		</h1>
		<p slot="content"><a href="#interview" style="color: blue"><strong>( I didn't get the job )</strong></a></p>
	</HeroBanner>
	<PageSection
		id="interview"
		data-section-color="yellow"
		background-color="yellow"
		full-height
		width="1200"
	>
		<h2 class="text-4xl">It's true.</h2>
		<p class="text-xl"><span class="font-bold">Interviewer</span>: What do you value in teammates?</p>
		<p class="text-xl"><span class="font-bold">Dummy</span>: I value a healthy team culture over all else. I love working with passionate people that love building cool <span class="highlight"><sup>*</sup>sh!t</span>!</p>
		<p class="text-md text-center font-bold">*oops</p>
	</PageSection>

	<PageSection
		id="recruiter"
		data-section-color="lightblue"
		background-color="lightblue"
		full-height
		width="1200"
	>
		<h2 class="text-4xl">Note from my recruiter.</h2>
		<p class="text-xl">"They thought you had a great skill set for the position, but because of the curse word I wouldn't be a good fit culturally."</p>
		<p>Love, Jacob the Recruiter</p>
	</PageSection>
	<PageSection
		data-section-color="lightgreen"
		background-color="lightgreen"
		full-height
		width="1200"
	>
		<h2 class="text-4xl">NOW LET ME BE CLEAR.</h2>
		<p class="text-lg">I was definitely disappointed that I didn't get the position. It really did seem like it would be a good fit and the person that interviewed me was super cool.</p>
		<p class="text-lg">I also for sure understand where they are coming from and hold no ill will or resentments towards the company and their values at all.</p>
		<p class="text-lg">I am more just disappointed in myself. When I get excited about a topic sometimes I drop a curse word.</p>
		<p></p>
	</PageSection>

	<PageSection
		data-section-color="black"
		data-section-theme="dark"
		background-color="black"
		full-height
		width="1200"
	>
		<div class="text-light">
			<h2 class="text-hero">But...</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-wrap">If you're looking for a passionate Vue, Nuxt, UI, UX, Astro, WordPress, Prismic, What-else-you-got frontend developer that says <span class="highlight-yellow">Shit</span> every now and then hit me up!</p>
			<div class="text-center">
				<a class="text-fluid-md" href="mailto:nickberens360@gmail.com">nickberens360@gmail.com</a>
			</div>

		</div>
	</PageSection>

</Layout>
